I joined MJ Lee and CNN alongside Liz, Jess, and Dani to talk honestly about the DOJ’s release of the Epstein files, the redactions, the omissions, and the impact on survivors.

What was released matters. 
What was withheld matters more.

Thank you, MJ, for holding space and letting survivors speak.

